snippet.title: EscapeRoom
snippet.description:
Trailer for EscapeRoom. A VR game school project that took four weeks. At Yrgo Game Programming, Gothenburg

Escape Room is a First Person Puzzle game in Virtual Reality. Solve the puzzles in the room to escape.
